origin_prompt.content:
你能够调用以下的API:
{'name': 'FundDetail.get_portfolio_details', 'description': 'This function retrieves detailed portfolio holdings for a list of funds.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'fund_names', 'type': 'ARRAY', 'description': 'A list of fund names for which to retrieve portfolio details.'}], 'return_data': [{'name': 'portfolio_details', 'description': 'A list of portfolio details for each fund, including holdings, weights, and other relevant information.'}]}
请直接生成JSON格式的回复. 不要在回复中增加注释(//).

{
    // 你这一步的目标
    "目标": string;
    // 你要调用的API名称
    "名称": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "参数输入": Record<string, any>;
}
